{"tid":2134664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於寄不明種子去外國，我認為係一班小粉紅自發做嘅","createTime":"2020-08-01T01:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T06:39:18.000Z","uid":57376,"like":11,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"03802372a6bfece7649f5accb1b582839a47784b","tid":2134664,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:34:51.000Z","msg":"以中共嘅間諜規模根本唔需要用啲咁引人注目嘅方法去破壞外國生態，咁對佢一啲好處都無，反而班愛國仇外嘅小粉紅可能會因為近年經濟轉差、糧食失收，再加上戰狼思想，就會諗到用呢種低成本低技術低風險嘅方法去報「國仇家恨」，而小粉紅有一個共通點就係每次都唔考慮到佢啲行為會連累國家形象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1396b47943580d99d41c6edc6b240ac6b378d31f","tid":2134664,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:37:06.000Z","msg":"宜家嘅問題係班小粉紅到底可以造到乜野生化種子？定係只不過天然具入侵性嘅植物？"},{"pid":"7567cc6a523d354f33ad6b996df75ec6bdef354e","tid":2134664,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"#chinatoxicseeds"},{"pid":"583ddac56a9637cd30339d02ea969b833ef37ad9","tid":2134664,"uid":25468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"咁大規模嘅「自發」行為，共產黨係唔會容許的，唔好咁天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60aebca59cf4b331a838d69a03e64497f992efd8","tid":2134664,"uid":10652,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"你都戇撚鳩<br />\n你試下自發係一個地方寄咁多件出去<br />\n會唔會唔比人周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efab873b5dd693d281764da8315b067417ee5b43","tid":2134664,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60aebca59cf4b331a838d69a03e64497f992efd8","tid":2134664,"uid":10652,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"你都戇撚鳩<br />\n你試下自發係一個地方寄咁多件出去<br />\n會唔會唔比人周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"低能<br />\n支那網購班店主一日發幾多貨出去<img src=\"/assets/f